===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|πτερόν||wing, feather}} + {{m|grc|ποδός}}, genitive singular of {{m|grc|πούς||foot, leg}}. See also {{m|en|ptero-}}, {{m|en|-pod}}.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Any of several small [[marine]] [[gastropod]] [[mollusk]]s, of the suborder ''{{taxlink|Thecosomata|suborder|noshow=1}}'', that have winglike lobes on the feet; a [[sea butterfly]].

